column2: SELECT Top # G.cx, G.cy, G.cz, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, G.objID, G.modelMag_u, G.modelMag_g, p.petroR5#_g, p.petroR5#_u, p.petroR5#_r, p.petroR5#_i, p.petroR5#_z, G.ra, G.dec FROM GALAXY as G JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = G.objid JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE ( Flags & (g.fPhotoFlags(&&&) +  g.fPhotoFlags(&&&) +  g.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) ) = # and g.petroRad_r < # and ((modelMag_u - modelMag_g) - (psfMag_u - psfMag_g)) > #
